I promise,

57:53.637 --> 57:55.804
but right now,
we really have to hurry.

57:55.806 --> 57:57.706
- What are you talking about?

57:57.708 --> 57:59.107
- Come on.

57:59.109 --> 58:00.809
- Oh, man. Fuck.

58:06.983 --> 58:09.251
He's not answering.

58:09.253 --> 58:10.986
What do we do, text him?

58:10.988 --> 58:12.721
- Yeah, just--
just fucking text him.

58:12.723 --> 58:14.656
I want to know what he's doing.

58:20.196 --> 58:21.864
- Unlock the goddamn door!

58:24.634 --> 58:26.668
All right.

58:26.670 --> 58:28.270
Found out
something you want to know,

58:28.272 --> 58:30.572
but first, tell me what
you've been hiding about Nicole.

58:32.575 --> 58:33.609
Huh?

58:33.611 --> 58:34.943
- Tell him.

58:34.945 --> 58:38.614
- Amber and Nicole
weren't crazy, okay?

58:38.616 --> 58:41.016
S-Something was after them.

58:41.018 --> 58:42.918
- Something named Morgan?

58:44.287 --> 58:45.921
- How did you know that?

58:45.923 --> 58:48.524
- This was Amber's.

58:48.526 --> 58:50.125
Okay, it says spirits

58:50.127 --> 58:51.994
