59:00.037 --> 59:02.905
- Okay, her grandmother said
she wanted to keep Morgan

59:02.907 --> 59:04.740
somewhere safe, right?

59:04.742 --> 59:06.108
- Yeah.

59:06.110 --> 59:08.610
- Well, if she believed
in this cold-iron thing,

59:08.612 --> 59:10.145
I know where they went.

59:11.881 --> 59:13.916
- All right,
then hit the gas, Magneto.

59:13.918 --> 59:16.251
- No. No,
someone has to stay behind

59:16.253 --> 59:17.819
