left her alone,

01:03:06.283 --> 01:03:08.383
but she was never lonely.

01:03:08.385 --> 01:03:11.253
She could feel their presence.

01:03:13.389 --> 01:03:17.292
When she got older,
she wanted to have friends.

01:03:32.441 --> 01:03:35.977
That doctor told her
to use the computer,

01:03:35.979 --> 01:03:39.414
