a way to reach out.

01:03:42.285 --> 01:03:45.353
At first, it seemed good.

01:03:45.355 --> 01:03:47.422
- Then the picture.

01:04:04.207 --> 01:04:09.110
- And at the end,
she wasn't hurting just herself.

01:04:18.254 --> 01:04:20.522
A psychiatrist
couldn't save her.

01:04:21.624 --> 01:04:26.428
I took her back here
to try myself.

01:04:29.265 --> 01:04:34.336
I tried everything I knew
to help her...

01:04:34.338 --> 01:04:36.605
- [ Morgan yelling ]
- to get inside her mind...

01:04:37.974 --> 01:04:39.641
and quiet her.

01:04:42.144 --> 01:04:44.379
[ no audible dialogue ]

01:04:44.381 --> 01:04:46.514
But I couldn't.

01:04:48.651 --> 01:04:52.053
Then I lost her.

01:04:57.059 --> 01:05:02.163
I told myself her pain was over,
she was free.

01:05:03.432 --> 01:05:06.067
I don't know
what else I could have done.

01:05:07.904 --> 01:05:11.940
- Something's changed.

01:05:11.942 --> 01:05:15.543
Morgan's not the same girl
that she was when she was alive,

01:05:15.545 --> 01:05:19.180
and, Maya, I need
to find out what happened.

01:05:19.182 --> 01:05:21.449
- And how we can make her stop.

01:05:27.256 --> 01:05:30.191
- There is one thing...

01:05:32.061 --> 01:05:35.230
but I can't do it alone.

01:05:44.006 --> 01:05:45.707
[ lantern clatters ]

01:06:08.097 --> 01:06:09.664
- Is this a séance?

01:06:10.967 --> 01:06:13.034
- Kristen will enter a trance.

01:06:26.048 --> 01:06:29.050
Morgan has chosen you.

01:06:31.053 --> 01:06:34.089
She has entered your mind,

01:06:34.091 --> 01:06:36.658
and now you will enter hers.

01:06:40.196 --> 01:06:42.564
[ ringing echoes ]

01:06:50.740 --> 01:06:52.774
Give me your hands.

01:06:56.078 --> 01:06:57.779
Close your eyes.

01:06:59.248 --> 01:07:01.249
[ wind blowing ]

01:07:02.585 --> 01:07:08.623
