01:11:09.966 --> 01:11:12.267
- What, for her?

01:11:12.269 --> 01:11:15.370
What about us?
She's gonna kill us!

01:11:15.372 --> 01:11:18.406
- Whoa, what are you
talking about, "us"?

01:11:18.408 --> 01:11:21.576
